acceptOwnership().details: The new owner accepts the ownership transfer.

launchAgent((string,string,string,string.details: Requires msg.value to cover nad.fun's deploy fee (10 MON) plus any initial buy cost.      The ERC-8004 NFT is minted to this contract and immediately transferred to msg.sender.      Any tokens from an initial buy are also forwarded to msg.sender.      Excess MON is refunded.

linkToken(uint256,address).details: Caller must own the ERC-8004 NFT for the given agentId.

params.agentId: The agent to link the token to.

onERC721Received(address,address,uint256.details: Required to receive ERC-721 tokens via safeTransferFrom / safeMint.      Only accepts NFTs from the identity registry to prevent griefing.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

pendingOwner().details: Returns the address of the pending owner.

params.agentURI: IPFS/HTTPS URI to the agent registration JSON.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Starts the ownership transfer of the contract to a new account. Replaces the pending transfer if there is one. Can only be called by the current owner. Setting `newOwner` to the zero address is allowed; this can be used to cancel an initiated ownership transfer.

updateAgentWallet(uint256,address).details: Does NOT update the ERC-8004 agentWallet  do that via the identity registry.

updateEndpoint(uint256,string).details: The caller must own the ERC-8004 NFT. To update the agentURI on ERC-8004,      call `identityRegistry.setAgentURI()` directly (you own the NFT).

agentExists(uint256).notice: Check whether an agent exists in this factory.

deactivateAgent(uint256).notice: Deactivate an agent (mark as not operational).

getAgent(uint256).notice: Get full agent info by agentId.

getAgentByToken(address).notice: Get agent info by its linked nad.fun token address.

getAgentReputation(uint256).notice: Get the agent's aggregated reputation from ERC-8004.

getAgentsByCreator(address).notice: List all agentIds created by a given address.

getTokenProgress(uint256).notice: Get the bonding curve progress for an agent's token (0  1e18).

isAgentToken(address).notice: Check if a token is linked to any agent in this factory.

isTokenGraduated(uint256).notice: Check if the agent's token has graduated to the DEX.

launchAgent((string,string,string,string.notice: One-click launch: register ERC-8004 identity + deploy nad.fun token + link them.

linkToken(uint256,address).notice: Link a pre-existing nad.fun token to a registered agent.

pause().notice: Pause all launch/register operations. Does not affect reads or updates.

registerAgent(string,string).notice: Register an ERC-8004 identity only (no token). Useful when the creator already has         a nad.fun token or doesn't want one yet.

totalAgents().notice: Total number of agents launched through this factory.

updateAgentWallet(uint256,address).notice: Update the wallet that receives x402 revenue for this agent.

updateEndpoint(uint256,string).notice: Update the agent's API endpoint stored in this factory.
